            <lg xml:id="TK499">
<l>ciṟainalaṉuñ cīru milareṉiṉu mānta</l>
<l>ruṟainilattō ṭoṭṭa laritu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is a hazardous thing to attack men in their own country, although they may neither have power nor a good fortress.</l>
